# Development Workflow

Every task follows the same workflow. For the full platform workflow including model routing and agents, see `workflow/00-workflow.mdc`.

## Steps

0. Load project state — read `.cursor/project-management/` and `PROJECT_ROADMAP.md`
1. Understand the request
2. Analyze the project — run `/context-loading`
3. Locate existing implementation
4. Identify reusable components
5. Create a plan — run `/model-routing` for model selection
6. Implement
7. Validate — run `/verifier` for significant features
8. Run required checks
9. Update documentation if necessary
10. Update project management state — `PROJECT_STATUS`, `TASKS`, `HANDOFF`, `CURRENT_CONTEXT`
11. Summarize: what changed, why, risks, next steps